wsdl:definitions.wsdl:documentation: The web service fascade for the Blackbaud Application Framework operations

wsdl:operation.name: AdHocQueryDelete
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Deletes a Query from the Ad-Hoc Query table

wsdl:operation.name: AdHocQueryGetDefinition
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the query definition and a list of query fields used for the given ID

wsdl:operation.name: AdHocQueryGetDefinitionForDataList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the query definition and a list of query fields used to create the data list for the given data list ID

wsdl:operation.name: AdHocQueryGetIDByName
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the query system ID given the name

wsdl:operation.name: AdHocQueryRefreshStaticIDSet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Refreshes the set of IDs in a Static Selection.

wsdl:operation.name: AdHocQuerySave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Validates and saves a query definition object to the database

wsdl:operation.name: AdHocQuerySaveDataList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Creates or updates a data list based on ad-hoc query metadata and adds it to the catalog so it can be consumed by other areas of the application.

wsdl:operation.name: BatchDefaultsLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the value translations for a dataformitem containing default fields for a batch given the formfields that make up the batch

wsdl:operation.name: BatchLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the data (for edit or view) for a batch defined by the supplied batch ID

wsdl:operation.name: BatchSave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Saves the data (for edit or view) for a batch defined by the supplied batch ID

wsdl:operation.name: BatchTemplateGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the metadata for the specified batch template ID

wsdl:operation.name: BatchValidate
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Validates the data for a batch defined by the supplied batch ID

wsdl:operation.name: BusinessProcessGenerateActiveXScript
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Generates an ActiveX script which can be executed to launch a business process

wsdl:operation.name: BusinessProcessInformation
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns information on a given business process type

wsdl:operation.name: BusinessProcessOutputLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Loads data from a business process output table.

wsdl:operation.name: CatalogBrowserGetCatalogItem
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the requested catalog item

wsdl:operation.name: CatalogBrowserGetCatalogResource
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the contents of the requested catalog resource.

wsdl:operation.name: CatalogBrowserGetDependencyTree
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the dependency tree for the given catalog item

wsdl:operation.name: CatalogBrowserGetItemByID
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the requested loaded catalog item definition from the database.

wsdl:operation.name: CatalogBrowserGetItems
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the available catalog items

wsdl:operation.name: CatalogBrowserLoadCatalogItem
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Loads/updates the given catalog item

wsdl:operation.name: CodeTableEntryAdd
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Creates a new CodeTable entry item

wsdl:operation.name: CodeTableEntryDelete
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Deletes a CodeTable entry item

wsdl:operation.name: CodeTableEntryGetData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the data for an individual code table entry item

wsdl:operation.name: CodeTableEntryGetDescription
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the description for the given code table ID.

wsdl:operation.name: CodeTableEntryGetID
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the ID for the given table entry.

wsdl:operation.name: CodeTableEntryGetList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the list of table entries for the given code table.

wsdl:operation.name: CodeTableEntryUpdate
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Updates a CodeTable entry description and active status

wsdl:operation.name: CodeTableGetDescription
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the user-friendly name for the given code table name.

wsdl:operation.name: CodeTableGetLookupInfo
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns information such as user permissions for the given code table name.

wsdl:operation.name: CountryGetFormats
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves formatting information for all countries.

wsdl:operation.name: CountryStateGetID
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the ID for the given country and state.

wsdl:operation.name: DashboardGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the metadata that defines the dashboard

wsdl:operation.name: DataFormGetDropDownValueList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of DataFormDropDownValue rows for the given DataForm

wsdl:operation.name: DataFormInstanceGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the data form definition for a given data form name or ID.

wsdl:operation.name: DataFormLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the data (for edit or view) for a record defined by the supplied Form ID

wsdl:operation.name: DataFormSave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Saves (insert or update) the data for a record defined by the supplied Form ID

wsdl:operation.name: DataListGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the data list ouptut definition and parameter form definition given the name or ID

wsdl:operation.name: DataListLoadMore
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Loads a window of rows from a previous call to DataListLoad which had more TotalAvailableRows than the TotalRequestRows in the reply. Used to support paging of data in large result sets.

wsdl:operation.name: SimpleDataListGetTranslation
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the translation text for a simple datalist entry ID

wsdl:operation.name: SimpleDataListLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the data for a simple datalist given the ID or Name and any parameters

wsdl:operation.name: GlobalChangeInformation
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns information on a given global change definition

wsdl:operation.name: GlobalChangeList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of all available global changes.

wsdl:operation.name: GlobalChangeParametersLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the saved parameters for a global change instance.

wsdl:operation.name: IDMap
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Maps an ID of one record type to an ID of another record type. Can also be used to map the current AppUserID to an associated ID of a particular record type.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiDashboardGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the metadata for the pages, tabs, and KPI instances a user has chosen for his personalized KPI dashboard.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiDashboardSave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Saves the pages, tabs, and KPI instances a user has chosen for his personalized KPI dashboard.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves a KPI catalog item from the database.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiGetTree
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of KPI catalog items to be displayed in a tree view.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiInstanceDelete
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Deletes a KPI instance from the database.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiInstanceGetIDByName
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the KPI instance system ID given the name

wsdl:operation.name: KpiInstanceGetListByKpiCatalogID
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of KPI instances for a given KPI catalog item.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiInstanceGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves a KPI instance from the database.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiInstanceGetStatus
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the value along with the variance, percent of goal, etc. for a KPI instance based on the provided KPI instance ID.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiInstanceGetTree
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of KPI instances to be displayed in a tree view.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiInstanceSave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Saves a KPI instance to the database.

wsdl:operation.name: MergeTaskGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves a MergeTask catalog item from the database.

wsdl:operation.name: PageDefinitionGetListByRecordType
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of page definitions based on a given record type. The list will also be filtered by pages containing expression data forms to which the current user has rights (where applicable).

wsdl:operation.name: PageDefinitionGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the metadata for a page definition given the ID or Name

wsdl:operation.name: QueryViewGetLookUpValues
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of lookup values for a query field

wsdl:operation.name: QueryViewGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the query view field definitions given the name or ID.

wsdl:operation.name: QueryViewGetRootList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of query view root objects.

wsdl:operation.name: QueryViewGetTree
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the initial query design tree for the given query type or root query object

wsdl:operation.name: QueryViewGetTreeNode
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a query tree node given the query view path

wsdl:operation.name: RecordOperationGetPrompt
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves the prompt as defined by the supplied Record Operation name or ID

wsdl:operation.name: RecordOperationPerform
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Performs the operation on a record as defined by the supplied Record Operation name or ID

wsdl:operation.name: ReportRootFoldersGetList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves a list of Report Services root folders.

wsdl:operation.name: ReportsGenerateReportModel
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Generates a report model based on the provided query view metadata.

wsdl:operation.name: ReportsGetDataSource
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves the fully qualified Report Service data source name for this database.

wsdl:operation.name: ReportsGetReportSpec
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves the Report Specification

wsdl:operation.name: ReportsGetReportSpecByName
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves the Report Specification By Name

wsdl:operation.name: ReportsGetURLs
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves the Report Web Service and Report Rendering Engine URLs

wsdl:operation.name: ReportsPublishServerReportToCatalog
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Creates a report spec for a report that only exists on the SQL Server report server and loads that spec to the catalog. This web service is used primarily to enable a report created by a user-generated report model to be used by Page Designer.

wsdl:operation.name: SearchListGetList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of search list entries given the record type

wsdl:operation.name: SearchListGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the search list field definitions and filter form definition given the name or ID.

wsdl:operation.name: SearchListGetTranslation
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the translation text for a search list entry ID

wsdl:operation.name: GetADGroupSid
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the Active Directory group sid given the group name

wsdl:operation.name: SecurityGetRoleFeaturePermTree
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns information the granted and denied features for a specific System Role.

wsdl:operation.name: SecurityUserGrantedFeature
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Used to determine if the requesting user has been granted (and not denied) a feature in a system role.

wsdl:operation.name: SyncRoleUsers
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Adds users in the supplied userXML into the role defined by the supplied role ID

wsdl:operation.name: SelectionGetQueryInfo
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the type of query (Ad-hoc or Smart) that a selection is based on.

wsdl:operation.name: CurrentUserInfoGet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns information about the calling user.

wsdl:operation.name: GetAvailableREDatabases
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the list of RE databases that are available.

wsdl:operation.name: GetFiscalYearLastMonth
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the FISCALYEARLASTMONTH value from the INSTALLATIONINFO table.

wsdl:operation.name: GetFormatPhonesSetting
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the FORMATPHONES value from the INSTALLATIONINFO table.

wsdl:operation.name: PingSimple
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Trivial Web Service method that returns a string passed to it

wsdl:operation.name: Ping
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Used to test availability of the service.

wsdl:operation.name: ServiceInfoGetVersionNumber
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the current version of the Service. As the service evolves this number will increment

wsdl:operation.name: ServiceInfoGetVersionInfo
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the current version of the Service and information about the OS and framework version the service is running on.

wsdl:operation.name: ServiceInfoGet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns various server properties such as version information.

wsdl:operation.name: SessionEndOneWay
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Releases session state associated with the user.

wsdl:operation.name: SessionEnd
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Releases session state associated with the user.

wsdl:operation.name: SessionStart
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a session key to be used to maintain client state between calls to the service.

wsdl:operation.name: ShellGetAllTasks
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns information about all tasks and their respective functional areas defined in the system.

wsdl:operation.name: ShellGetNavigation
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the navigation tree for the current user, which is used to build the Shell UI.

wsdl:operation.name: SmartFieldInformation
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns information on a given smart field definition

wsdl:operation.name: SmartFieldList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of all available smart fields.

wsdl:operation.name: SmartFieldParametersLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the saved parameters for a smart field instance.

wsdl:operation.name: SmartQueryGetList
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a list of smart query entries given the record type

wsdl:operation.name: SmartQueryGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the smart query field definitions and filter form definition given the name or ID.

wsdl:operation.name: SmartQueryInstanceDelete
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Deletes the smart query instance given the smart query instance ID.

wsdl:operation.name: SmartQueryInstanceGetIDByName
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the smart query instance system ID given the name

wsdl:operation.name: SmartQueryInstanceGetMetaData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the data input by a user for a Smart Query

wsdl:operation.name: SmartQueryInstanceSave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Saves the data input by a user for a Smart Query

wsdl:operation.name: SmartQueryRefreshStaticIDSet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Refreshes the set of IDs in a Static Selection created from a Smart query.

wsdl:operation.name: BatchSettingsGet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the set of user settings available for a given batch type.

wsdl:operation.name: BatchSettingsSave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Saves the batch settings defined by the current application user for a given batch type.

wsdl:operation.name: ShellSettingsGet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the set of user settings available for the shell application.

wsdl:operation.name: ShellSettingsSave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Saves the shell settings defined by the current application user

wsdl:operation.name: UserFavoritesGet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the favorites defined for the current application user

wsdl:operation.name: UserFavoritesSave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Saves the favorites defined by the current application user

wsdl:operation.name: UserHomePageGet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the home page defined for the current application user

wsdl:operation.name: UserHomePageSave
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Saves the home page defined by the current application user

wsdl:operation.name: UserMultiPageHistoryGet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the page history defined for the current application user for the given set of pages

wsdl:operation.name: UserPageHistoryGet
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the page history defined for the current application user

wsdl:operation.name: AdHocQueryProcess
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the results for the given query ID or query definition

wsdl:operation.name: BusinessProcessLaunch
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Launches a given business process

wsdl:operation.name: DashboardGetData
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the dataset for the given Dashboard ID

wsdl:operation.name: DataListLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Loads the data for a datalist given the ID or Name and any parameters

wsdl:operation.name: KpiGetDynamicGoalValue
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the goal value for a KPI which uses a stored procedure to calculate the goal value using a set of parameters defined in the KPI spec.

wsdl:operation.name: KpiGetValue
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the value of a KPI based on the provided parameters.

wsdl:operation.name: RSSGetFeed
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns an RSS feed for the given datalistID.

wsdl:operation.name: SearchListLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the data for a search list given the search list ID or Name and any filters

wsdl:operation.name: SmartQueryLoad
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the data for a smart query given the smart query ID or Name and any filters

wsdl:operation.name: PingSimple
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Trivial Web Service method that returns a string passed to it

wsdl:operation.name: ServiceInfoGetVersionNumber
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the current version of the Service. As the service evolves this number will increment

wsdl:operation.name: ServiceInfoGetVersionInfo
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns the current version of the Service and information about the OS and framework version the service is running on.

wsdl:service.name: AppFxWebService
wsdl:service.wsdl:documentation: The web service fascade for the Blackbaud Application Framework operations
